                            <comment id="14948" author="darren.davison" created="Wed, 12 Oct 2005 11:09:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Markus, &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;could you give this a go and let me know if it works for you please?  You now can specify a List of templateLoaders on the FM config, so for example, the following should work:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;bean id=&quot;fmConfig&quot; class=&quot;...FreeMarkerConfigurer&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;property name=&quot;templateLoaders&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;list&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;ref local=&quot;myFileTemplateLoader&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;ref local=&quot;myDatabaseTemplateLoader&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/list&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks,&lt;br/&gt;
Darren.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15256" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Fri, 4 Nov 2005 07:30:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This has already been added for 1.2.6, as the consequence of another report. Please give a recent nightly 1.2.6 snapshot a try!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
